Package: aricode
Type: Package
Title: aricode: a package for efficient computations of standard clustering comparison measures
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Julien Chiquet, Guillem Rigaill
Maintainer: Julien Chiquet <julien.chiquet@inra.fr>
Description: Implements an efficient O(n) algorithm based on bucket-sorting for fast computation of standard clustering comparison measures (RI, ARI, NID, NVI, NMI, entropy) as described in Vinh et al (2009) <https://doi.org/10.1145/1553374.1553511>.
License: GPL (>=3)
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    Matrix,
    Rcpp
Suggests: testthat
LinkingTo: Rcpp
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
